      }, {
        "text": " {\"type\": \"string\"}\n  }\n}\n"
      }, {
        "text": "```\n\n### 3. Multisig Deploy Webhook (Python"
      }, {
        "text": "/Flask Pseudocode)\n"
      }, {
        "text": "```"
      }, {
        "text": "python\nfrom flask import Flask, request, jsonify\n\napp \u003d Flask(__name__)\n#"
      }, {
        "text": " WARNING: Pseudocode. Production requires a proper DB and HSM integration.\nrequests_db \u003d {}\napprovals_db"
      }, {
        "text": " \u003d {}\n\n@app.route(\u0027/request_deploy\u0027, methods\u003d[\u0027POST\u0027])\ndef request_deploy():\n    "
      }, {
